site-title: Sali idlisen seg uɣbaṛ n Internet
debug-notice: Asmel-agi yella deg uskar n temseɣtayṭ, ihi yezmer ur iteddu ara akken iwata.
login-notice: Yessefk ad teqqneḍ akken ad tessaliḍ idlisen ar Wikimedia Commons
site-explanation: Wagi d afecku n usali IA, ma ualc aɣilif, azen-d yal ugur.
form-label-ia-id: Asulay n ufaylu n iɣbaṛen n Internet:
ia-id-help: Asulay d aḥric n tensa URL deffir 'details/', amedya: $1
commons-name-help: Isem ara tmuddeḍ i ufaylu ticki yuli ar Wikimedia Commons. Ma yella afaylu yella yakan, ur yettwazan ara tikelt nniḍen ihi ad tettwaɛerḍeḍ ad tbeddleḍ dagi.
job-queue-empty: Adras n umahil d ilem akka tura.
jobs-will-be-removed: Tiwuriyin ad ttwakksent si tebdart-agi ticki fukent udiɣ ma ifuk usali ar commons.
user-contribs-link: Ifuyla ad d-banen deg tebdart-ik n uttekki di Commons.
file-source-help:
Seg wanida i yessefk ad d-sirweɣ afaylu DjVu ?
Ẓer d akken i JP2 d PDF, talɣut-ik n usesteb ad tettwasekles ɣef uqeddac n Tool Labs ddeqs n wakud ilaqen arama yettwaselket (di tanumi, ddaw n 30 n tisdatin). Tzemreḍ ad tekkseḍ anekcum n ufecku-agi melmi tebɣiḍ.
remove-first-page-help: Kra n inefraḍen n Google gebren asebter n tduli yettwaḥerzen s izerfan, ayen ur yettwasirgen ara di Commons. Ugar n isallen, Wali asebter n tallelt di Wikisource.
authorize-first: Yessefk ad tsirgeḍ asali IA send asali n ufaylu
upload-time-warning: (Ɣuṛ-k: asali yezmer ad yawi ugar n tesdat!)
invalid-commons-name: '$1' mačči d isem n ufaylu ameɣtu i Wikimedia Commons
no-found-on-ia: '$1' mačči d asulay ameɣtu n n uɣbaṛ Internet
already-on-commons: Isem n ufaylu '$1' yella yakkan di Wikimedia Commons
creator-template-missing: Ameskar '$1' ur ɣur-s ara taneɣruft amernay. Ma yella tesneḍ asulay-is ID Wikidata, tzemreḍ ad ternuḍ taneɣruft tura.
